<!-- ========== DESCRIPTION CARD ========== -->
<section class="srv-meaning" id="srv-meaning">
  <div class="about-section-container">
    <div class="srv-meaning-card" data-reveal="up" data-reveal-delay="200">
      <p>NBFC work is not just "filing." It's readiness, governance, documentation discipline, and clean execution. Most delays and penalties happen because the NBFC route is not mapped correctly, the business plan and internal system is not ready, or compliance is running without a calendar and ownership tracker. We help you build clarity first, then execute in a predictable way.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

